 would say equal to the Grand Slams.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not put it above or below, just because I have never played before.\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my first time,\\\" Gauff said earlier this year.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, I always want to do well, try to get a medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff and James, the 39-year-old leading scorer in NBA history, both compete in sports that are outside the traditional Olympic world and enjoy attention year-round, not just every four years.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999968391868992, \"rank\": 3.14809029496024e-06, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauff made the American team for the Tokyo Games three years ago as a teenager, but had to sit out that edition after testing positive for COVID-19 right before she was due to fly to Japan.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999905318659634, \"rank\": 5.645920131703159e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999607297957732, \"rank\": 2.984847031358107e-05, \"text\": \"COVID-19\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pande